description: This file serves as the entry point for a React web application, rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports core React libraries, styling, and the main App component, then initializes and renders the app within a strict mode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React application into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the specified DOM node.
